</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-04-02-0205-0002-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-04-02-0205-0002-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>See 7 <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ William Waller Hening, ed. &lt;i&gt;The Statutes at Large; Being a Collection of All the Laws of Virginia, from the First Session of the Legislature, in the Year 1619&lt;/i&gt;. 13 vols. 181923. Reprint. Charlottesville, Va., 1969. ]">Hening</span> 8792 for the text of the act which is in much the same language as the commission.</p>

